  "title": "AIR-CONDITIONING MAINTENANCE TECHNICIAN",
  "description": "<ul><li>To perform air-conditioning maintenance, general cleaning, jet wash, chemical wash, chemical overhaul, troubleshooting, and etc.</li><li>Responsible for inspecting job sites for proper ACMV air-conditioning maintenance.</li><li>To attend to the client’s complaints promptly.</li><li>To resolve problems efficiently without unnecessary delay.</li><li>To be involved in the appointment of the Technicians</li><li>Train, instruct, and supervise the work of the Technicians</li><li>Ensure all works carried out by the Technicians, as set out in their Job Descriptions, are completed with due observation of appropriate Health & Safety requirements</li><li>Able to be hands-on when the situation requires, and any other responsibility as assigned by superiors.</li><li>And any other responsibility in the office as assigned by superiors.</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirement</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Diploma and above</li><li>A minimum of 5 years of experience as an Air Conditioning site supervisor or Foreman</li><li>Initiative and keenness to learn</li><li>Possesses strong analytical, interpersonal, and communication skills</li><li>Able to work in a fast-paced and stressful environment</li></ul>",
